      <br>• Electric cost: RM3/hour × 8 hours × 26 days = RM624/month
      <br><strong>Monthly Savings:</strong> RM2,496 per forklift</p>

      <p><strong>10-Forklift Fleet Annual Savings:</strong> RM299,520 in fuel costs alone.</p>

